# Web App Display Check URL

- For `project-manager/apps/web` startup and display checks, always use:
  - `http://dev-alrfy-ai.com:8001/`
- Do not use `http://localhost:3000/` or other ports as the primary verification URL.
- When launching dev server for checks, prefer external-host binding on port `8001` (e.g. LAN mode).
